      <title>“向这里开枪！”：记者向布拉格枪手尖叫以帮助人们逃离</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/shoot-here-reporter-screams-prague-gunman-help-people-flee-2023-12-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[“嘿，你这个混蛋，我在这儿，在这里开枪！”周四，一名捷克记者尖叫着试图分散一名枪手的注意力，这名枪手周四在布拉格一所大学大楼内杀害了 14 人，帮助人们逃离该国最严重的大规模枪击事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/shoot-here-reporter-screams-prague-gunman-help-people-flee-2023-12-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 18:08:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯完成92架外资飞机收购</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/russia-completes-buyouts-92-foreign-owned-planes-2023-12-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[航空公司和飞机租赁公司AerCap表示，俄罗斯已从外国租赁公司购买了另外92架飞机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/russia-completes-buyouts-92-foreign-owned-planes-2023-12-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 18:06:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前哥伦比亚士兵承认刺杀海地总统有罪</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/ex-colombian-soldier-pleads-guilty-haiti-presidents-assassination-2023-12-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五，一名前哥伦比亚士兵在美国法院承认了与他被指控参与 2021 年刺杀海地总统若弗内尔·莫伊兹有关的指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/ex-colombian-soldier-pleads-guilty-haiti-presidents-assassination-2023-12-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 17:50:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>古巴悄悄授权安乐死</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/cuba-quietly-authorizes-euthanasia-2023-12-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[古巴周五成为拉丁美洲和加勒比地区继哥伦比亚之后第二个授权安乐死的国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/cuba-quietly-authorizes-euthanasia-2023-12-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 17:32:40 GMT</pubDate>
